SIMD Floating-Point Exceptions¶

None

Other Exceptions¶

Non-EVEX-encoded instruction, see Exceptions Type 4.

EVEX-encoded VPACKSSDW, see Exceptions Type E4NF.

EVEX-encoded VPACKSSWB, see Exceptions Type E4NF.nb.

